	<article class="post-19459 post type-post status-publish hentry tag-cowen-tyler tag-labor-and-jobs tag-parenting tag-patient-protection-and-affordable-care-act-2010 tag-unemployment per-cowen-tyler des-labor-and-jobs des-parenting des-patient-protection-and-affordable-care-act-2010 des-unemployment" id="post-19459">
